R Notebook for the cystectomy study

Pascal Jerney

3rd May 2020

Prerequisites

Formulas

  • Indexed blood volume1: \(BV_i = \frac{70}{\sqrt{\frac{BMI}{22}}}\)2
  • Estimated blood volume: \(BV_e = BV_i * Weight\)3
  • Blood loss ratio: \(BL_r = \frac{BV_e}{BL_a}\)4
